patches/packages/glibc-solibs-2.17-i486-10_slack14.1.txz: Rebuilt.
patches/packages/glibc-zoneinfo-2014j-noarch-1.txz: Upgraded.
 Upgraded to tzcode2014j and tzdata2014j.
+--------------------------+");

